    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>diis de<lb break="no" n="3"/>abusque <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Cominius <lb n="5"/>Aphrodisius </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Zeile 6 befindet sich auf der crepido. Zahlreiche Ligaturen. Z. 3: VE-Ligatur; Z. 4: INI-Ligatur; Z. 5: HR-Ligatur, ODI-Ligatur, SI-Ligatur. An der Unterseite ein Dübelloch.</p>
            </div>
